question: ATTENTION TO THOSE WHO WILL USE LAB FACILITIES IN FKM (CALLED AS “LAB USERS”). -LAB USERS: UNDERGRAD AND POSTGRAD STUDENTS, FINAL YEAR PROJECT STUDENTS, RESEARCHERS, LECTURERS, VISITORS Awareness on safety and health is very important before using the lab facilities. Hence, you are required to ‘attend’ safety pass course in e-learning and take a test before entering the lab. You need to self-study by completing watching videos within 5 days. You can choose the date suggested in the google form.
answer: Registration for safety pass course in e-learning can be done through this link: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSevqlkHEQ-ZClJfkeRQHnh1Tmb7veESNIank3Qqd9TstSYFkg/viewform Detail information can be obtained in the safety pass website: https://mech.utm.my/safety-pass-fme/ You will get an email from the coordinator to confirm that your name has been enrolled in the elearning. If you don’t get any email within 5 days before your test, please send an email to rozlina@utm.my Thank You Regards, Rozlina Md Sirat FKM Safety Pass Coordinator 0137887801
